{"tid":2506860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"原來真係有豬兜CFO","createTime":"2021-04-27T14:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T06:45:48.000Z","uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f49a418bcd6eb5ac5659bf891257d416db2c5649","tid":2506860,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"奧園健康首席財務官令人大惑不解的投資<br />\n投資方是幾十億元市值的上市公司的首席財務官，應有專業知識，也不可能蠢到相信這種亂吹。<br />\n<br />\n此外，買過基金的人都知道，買入後，即時要付出交易費用，就是馬上贖回(redemption)，也肯定要付出代價，不可能全數收回投資，這也是常識。以上官司之所以發生，莫非沒寫明贖回條款？這實在不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n以上事件的奇怪點實在太多，又例如原告明明說涉及欺詐，報警不就了事嗎？為何又要花錢去打官司呢？八卦者也許要問知情人士，方可了解箇中實情了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%e5%a5%a7%e5%9c%92%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e9%a6%96%e5%b8%ad%e8%b2%a1%e5%8b%99%e5%ae%98%e4%bb%a4%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e6%83%91%e4%b8%8d%e8%a7%a3%e7%9a%84%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-265175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%2F%25e5%25a5%25a7%25e5%259c%2592%25e5%2581%25a5%25e5%25ba%25b7%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25b8%25ad%25e8%25b2%25a1%25e5%258b%2599%25e5%25ae%2598%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2583%2591%25e4%25b8%258d%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e7%259a%2584%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587-265175&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=454e915b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/%e5%a5%a7%e5%9c%92%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e9%a6%96%e5%b8%ad%e8%b2%a1%e5%8b%99%e5%ae%98%e4%bb%a4%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e6%83%91%e4%b8%8d%e8%a7%a3%e7%9a%84%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87-265175</a>"},{"pid":"396b89c2aa3b187a407c769c59229400257eb525","tid":2506860,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"條友會唔會係唔識呀"}]}